<head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><base href="&mvte:global:basehref;"><title>Learn About Sinister Blue</title><meta name="description" content="Learn what the Sinister Blue color trademark covers, why it exists and how it helps customers identify genuine diesel performance parts."><mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if><mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" /></head>
<body class="single-column"><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />
<main class="sd2-cp sd2-blue"><section class="sd2-policy__hero"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><nav class="sd2-policy__breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="&mvte:urls:SFNT:auto;">Home</a><span>/</span><span>Sinister Blue</span></nav><p class="sd2-cp__eyebrow">Brand protection / Clear answers</p><h1>Why blue<br>means Sinister.</h1><p>What the color registration covers, what it does not cover and why it helps protect diesel owners from counterfeit parts.</p><div class="sd2-cp__actions"><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="#blue-faq">Read the answers</a><a class="sd2-cp__button" href="identifying-genuine-sinister-parts.html">Identify genuine parts</a></div></div></section>
	<div class="sd2-cp__signal"><div><span>01</span><strong>Aftermarket parts</strong></div><div><span>02</span><strong>Products for resale</strong></div><div><span>03</span><strong>Consumer protection</strong></div></div>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section" id="blue-faq"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><div class="sd2-cp__section-head"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Sinister Blue explained</p><h2>Protection without the rumor.</h2></div><p>The registration is specific. Personal truck customization is not the target; consumer confusion from counterfeit resale products is.</p></div><mvt:item name="readytheme" param="contentsection( 'not-suing-over-blue' )" /></div></section>
</main><mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" /></body></html>
